            "bio": "Rabbi Esteban Gottfried is a Director, Playwright and actor and is the leader of <a title=\"Beit Tefilah Israeli\" href=\"http://www.btfila.org\">Beit Tefilah Israeli</a> (The Israeli House of Prayer) in Tel Aviv, which he founded with Rani Jaeger, and other friends.",
            "website": "http://gottfrieds.com",
